================================================================================
Acknowledgments
================================================================================

CIM Assessment Toolkit evolved from the Data Model Wrangler app by Nick von
Korff, which introduced a structured approach to assessing CIM data model
coverage in Splunk environments. Data Model Wrangler was itself inspired by
SA-cim_vladiator, developed by Vladimir and Splunk Works, which introduced
many of the original CIM validation concepts that remain foundational to
this work. We are grateful for the contributions of these authors.
